message.body: Hey Nate, Spielpalast has a fundraiser tonight, @muddy's at 8, spiel band at 930, do you want to join us? I can have charts printed for you. -gabi

Hey! Wish I could; I've got urinetown rehearsal 6:30-10:45... also, when/how can I get the book to you? I'm at the royal tyler theater every week night from those hours if you wanted to stop in and pick up the book, or i could drop it off somewhere?
